The paper deals with privacy attacks on web browsing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques for improving precision in website fingerprinting, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also uses image processing techniques to extract features from packet metadata, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the use of website fingerprinting attacks on network traffic, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
